6ï¸âƒ£ How Namespace works internally (API view)

Create namespace:

kubectl create ns dev


API request:

POST /api/v1/namespaces


Get pods in namespace:

kubectl get pods -n dev


API request:

GET /api/v1/namespaces/dev/pods

7ï¸âƒ£ YAML Example
